            "class": "EarthLike",
            "description": "Planet Tibur is an Earthlike jewel of blue oceans, mild seasons, and wide coastal continents dotted with tidy spaceports and vineyard belts. The capital, Alderport (invented name, derived from \u201cAlders Counsel\u201d), is famed for its sea-glass skyline, promenade districts, and festival calendar\u2014perfect for a relaxed layover that turns into a week."
